Root vault notes (`CLAUDE.md`, `GEMINI.md`, `PERPLEXITY.md`, `GROK.md`) are Obsidian entity notes about the agents ‚Äî wikilinks preserved, operational instructions live in dotfolders.

**Cross-tool auto-load at root:** `AGENTS.md` (pointer to `!/AGENTS.md`, auto-loaded by Codex/Copilot/Qodo).

**Machine-readable registry:** `swarm.json` at root (agents, personas, ecosystems, systems, protocols). `!/agents.json` also exists with a separate swarm-node structure.

**Microsoft context:** Logan has two MS identity contexts ‚Äî personal account and Idaho Public Television M365 institutional account (IPT IT policy applies). GitHub Copilot is a separate dev subscription linked to personal GitHub (`loganfinney27`).

**Linear Agent** (launched 2026-03-24): cloud-only AI in Linear workspace, no local dotfolder. In `swarm.json`.

## Capitalization Standard

- `ALL-CAPS.md` ‚Äî infrastructure/governance (CONSTITUTION.md, AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, CODEX.md, etc.)
- `Title Case.md` ‚Äî content vault notes (people, places, organizations, topics)
- `YYYY-MM-DD - Outlet - Title.md` ‚Äî dated sourced content
- `(YYYY) Type Number.md` ‚Äî bills
- `lowercase.ext` ‚Äî machine/config files (config.toml, settings.json, hooks.json)

